<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") -%>

<div class="row mt-5 mb-5 px-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5">
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted small">Last updated: March 13, 2026</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            
            <div class="legal-content fs-6 lh-lg">
                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h4>
                    <p>At VistaGo, we collect information to provide better services to all our users. This includes information you provide to us (like your name, email, and phone number) and information we collect as you use our services (like your IP address and browsing behavior).</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">2. How We Use Information</h4>
                    <p>We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, protect and improve our services, to develop new ones, and to protect VistaGo and our users. We also use this information to offer you tailored content—like giving you more relevant search results.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">3. Data Security</h4>
                    <p>We work hard to protect VistaGo and our users from unauthorized access to or unauthorized alteration, disclosure or destruction of information we hold. We restrict access to personal information to VistaGo employees, contractors and agents who need to know that information in order to process it for us.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">4. Contact Us</h4>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <span class="fw-bold">support@vistago.com</span>.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
